OL,3,CNursery fined after mouse droppings
OL,4,Cfound in children's playrooms
OL,6,FA nursery and its directors have been
OL,7,Ffined after mouse droppings were found
OL,8,Fthroughout the premises - including on
OL,9,Ftop of children's cups and bottles and
OL,10,Fin their playrooms.
OL,12,FCornerhouse Day Nursery Ltd, in Lees,
OL,13,FOldham, was prosecuted for food
OL,14,Fhygiene offences after officers found
OL,15,Fdirty appliances, and holes in the
OL,16,Fback of cupboards which were not pest-
OL,17,Fproofed.
