OL,3,CNursery fined after mouse droppings
OL,4,Cfound in children's playrooms
OL,6,FRodent droppings were found throughout
OL,7,Fthe nursery, including on top of open
OL,8,Fbags of pasta, on bibs, in boxes of
OL,9,Fchildren's cups and bottles, on work
OL,10,Fsurfaces and in the children's
OL,11,Fplayrooms.
OL,13,FDirt was found on the flooring and
OL,14,Fequipment, including the oven and the
OL,15,Fmicrowave, were found to be dirty.
