OL,4,Cfound in children's playrooms
OL,6,FThe directors and company pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to two charges under Food
OL,8,FSafety and Hygiene Regulations and
OL,9,Fwere sentenced at Tameside Magistrates
OL,10,FCourt on 22 November.
OL,12,FCornerhouse Day Nursery Ltd was fined
OL,13,Fa total of #2,000 with costs of #1,087
OL,14,Fand a victim surcharge of #800.
OL,16,FAlison O'Reilly was fined #380, with
OL,17,F#350 costs and victim surcharge of
OL,18,F#152 and her fellow director, Sadie
OL,19,FParsons, was also fined #461, with
OL,20,F#350 costs and victim surcharge of #184
