OL,3,CNursery fined after mouse droppings
OL,4,Cfound in children's playrooms
OL,6,FCouncillor Chris Goodwin said: "The
OL,7,Fsafety of our residents and their
OL,8,Fchildren is a priority for this
OL,9,Fadministration. This nursery
OL,10,Fpreviously had a five star rating for
OL,11,Ffood hygiene and safety.
OL,13,F"So, it's really disappointing that
OL,14,Fthey let standards fall so much.
OL,16,F"The building was very unclean and
OL,17,Fwe'd have been failing in our duties,
OL,18,Fespecially to the children and their
OL,19,Fparents, if we hadn't taken action.
OL,20,FThe business is continuing to make
OL,21,Fimprovements and that's good.
